                h3.section-title.notice Password Reset Request
                p.notice-text You recently requested to reset your password for your Duduintech account. We've received your request and are ready to help you regain access securely.

              .reset-section
                h3.reset-title Reset Your Password
                p.reset-instruction Click the button below to create a new password for your account. You'll be redirected to a secure page where you can set up your new credentials.

                a.reset-button(href="#{url}" role="button" aria-label="Reset your password securely") Reset My Password

                .info-card
                  .info-title Security Information
                  p.info-text This link is unique to your account and will expire for security reasons. If you need a new reset link, please visit our website to request another one.

