                h3.section-title.tips Security Best Practices
                ul.tips-list
                  li Choose a strong password with at least 8 characters
                  li Include a mix of uppercase, lowercase, numbers, and symbols
                  li Don't reuse passwords from other accounts
                  li Never share your password with anyone

